            "title": "盤中速報 - 鑫聯大投控(3709)股價拉至漲停，漲停價47.3元，成交4,327張",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>鑫聯大投控(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3709:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3709\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3709-TW</a>)03日11:38上漲4.3元，股價漲停報47.3元，委買7,000張、委賣75,000張，成交4,327張。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>主要業務為投資。管理。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>鑫聯大投控(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3709:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3709\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3709-TW</a>)近5日股價上漲1.42%，櫃買市場<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/TWS/TSE01\">加權指數</a>下跌0.07%，股價漲幅表現優於大盤。</p></section><section><p><em>近5日籌碼</em></p></section><!--$--><!--/$--><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>三大法人合計買賣超：+1,857 張</li> <li>外資買賣超：+1,713 張</li> <li>投信買賣超：0 張</li> <li>自營商買賣超：+144 張</li> <li>融資增減：+5 張</li> <li>融券增減：+10 張</li> </ul></section></main>",
